name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: Woody Allen’s newest movie features a middle-aged man who is sleeping with a 15-year-old girl. The movie will premiere at Cannes in May, and be entered into evidence in June.

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: President Trump had the JFK files declassified. Trump said, “I can take the class out of anything.”

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: A fast food restaurant in Australia is celebrating Halloween by offering a hamburger in a blue bun, sprinkled with real ants and worms. Or as Arby’s calls that, “The No. 6.”

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: During last night's 11-inning World Series game, a Dodgers fan got arrested after he jumped into one of the bullpens. Afterwards, the Dodgers admitted if the game had gone one more inning they would have needed him to pitch.
